for_developers/backends.md
     1‚Üí# Alternative backends
     3‚ÜíA "backend" is simply a program which `mdbook` will invoke during the book
     4‚Üírendering process. This program is passed a JSON representation of the book and
     5‚Üíconfiguration information via `stdin`. Once the backend receives this
     6‚Üíinformation it is free to do whatever it wants.
     7‚Üí
